Good morning, Superintendent Torlakson and board.

47:51.775 --> 47:53.037
It's great to see everyone.

47:53.077 --> 47:54.298
I love the smiling faces.

47:54.398 --> 47:54.958
It's great.

47:55.378 --> 47:58.561
It kind of feels kind of awkward being on this side, but very exciting.

47:58.741 --> 47:59.502
Very exciting.

