02:08:46.275 --> 02:08:47.875
So as leaders, you've done a great job.

02:08:47.895 --> 02:08:48.796
So thank you very much.

02:08:51.917 --> 02:08:52.437
Okay.

02:08:52.977 --> 02:08:53.958
Thank you for that.

02:08:54.118 --> 02:08:58.400
And I think we're ready for the next segment.

